Ingredients:
    Sausage x2
    Chili Pepper 3g
    Black Pepper 3g
    Potato x1
    Ketchup Pack x1
    Mayonnaise Pack x1
    Sunflower Oli 0.15lt
Steps:
    Season Sausage With
        Chili Pepper 3g
        Black Pepper 3g

    Grill
        Sausage x2


    Slice
        Potato (Gives Potato Slices)
        Potato Slices (Gives French Fries)

    Add to a Deep Fryer
        Sunflower Oil 0.15 lt

    Fry Using Deep Fryer
        French Fries

    Transfer to Plate
        French Fries x1
        Mayonnaise x1
        Ketchup x1
        Sausage x2

    Serve Hot